  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3145430/" class="title-link">从“道”、“无”与“德”看王弼和老子的政治哲学</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3145430"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/alanmirror/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1564438-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/alanmirror/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">littlebamboo</span>
