  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="3681782">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/3681782/" class="title-link">少年英才，光耀千古</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-3681782"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/insomiya/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u37183928-19.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/insomiya/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">立哥多无奈</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-09-14"
      class="main-meta">2010-09-14 09:46:21</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_3681782_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  王弼出身名门，年轻的时候就显示出过人的才气。尤其是他能够推翻陈腐观点，另辟蹊径。认为圣人体无，以孔子的不言无最为贵，可以说讲以无为本的玄学与当时的名教有了一点沟通。以至于往后影响了竹林七贤的思想。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
